article_title: Officials: WINhealth buyout won't affect Cheyenne Regional Medical Center
article_text:
Cheyenne, WY (82001)

Today

Partly cloudy with afternoon showers or thunderstorms. High 61F. Winds NE at 10 to 20 mph. Chance of rain 50%..

Tonight

Scattered thunderstorms during the evening, then cloudy skies overnight. Low 42F. Winds NNW at 10 to 15 mph. Chance of rain 50%.

article_metadata.author: Becky Orr

og.description: CHEYENNE - The state's takeover of WINhealth Partners Inc. will not affect operations at Cheyenne Regional Medical Center, hospital leaders said Friday.
